   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">This work instruction applies to all Space Plants that has FSC and Space IS Machines. This procedure helps to mitigate a problem with TCP/IP communication indicated when frequent COM-SOC II error messages occur during automatic or manual Saves from the sections (not MOC Save).</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">If the FSC shares the server with the PIC application (called a Combo system), this procedure should not be necessary because it is part of every upgrade. Consult the personnel responsible for the PIC to determine when the procedure was last performed.</li>
      </ol>
